2.3 Consumer prices index: fuel components: Figures include VAT where applicable.  VAT rates for coal and coke, gas, electricity and heating oils was 8% from the 2nd quarter of 1994 and 5% since the 4th quarter of 1997 (the rate changed on 1st September).
Real price series are deflated using GDP (market prices) deflator. GDP updated is updated when published by ONS.
Data may change regularly due to rebasing. The ONS use the latest full year of data as the base year and BEIS rebase to 2010=100.
Quarterly figures are available in the 2.1.1 tab and annual figures are avaliable in the 2.1.2 tab.
